-- Mercator Says Nova Ljubljanska Banka Deal Would Help Stabilize Ownership
-- B y   B o r i s   C e r n i
-- 2010-10-12T07:17:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-12/mercator-says-nova-ljubljanska-banka-deal-would-help-stabilize-ownership.html
Slovenian supermarket chain Mercator
Poslovni Sistem d.d. said a potential transaction between Nova
Ljubljanska Banka d.d. and Mid Europa Partners Ltd. to buy a
10.75 percent stake in Mercator would aid “the stabilization of
the ownership structure,” the company said in a filing to the
city stock exchange.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Boris Cerni in Ljubljana at 
 bcerni@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michelle E. Frazer at 
 mfrazer@bloomberg.net  